rComments: This is the absolute worst teacher on planet earth.

"Professor" Sweet doesn't teach enough variety of material to understand what Planning is. Uses her position to further her feminist political beliefs. Grading scale is horrible 92 is an "A" there are no "+" or "-" so a 91.5% earns a solid "B". If you want to know why water fountains are s exist, take this class, ridiculous. Hostile to students. F-

This class is required for Arch majors and may very well be helpful if you had another professor. Elizabeth Sweet requires many irrelevant readings that have little to do with an intro to Urban Planning course. She force-feeds her feminist/very liberal views upon students, not allowing students to conclude with their own opinions.

She is the worst professor I've had. She doesn't have text books and just puts up readings online which you are supposed to read. The mid-term and final are on compass and you get barely 1 hour to answer 4 essay questions. The class is ridiculous and she barely teaches anything and expects you to know all the material from the readings. DON'T even
